#summary Golf Markup Language Documentation: simpleType Angle180.

*[SAngle180 Angle180]*

  	

===  Super Types ===

double

===  Documentation ===
        
				Angle between -180 and 180 degrees.
		
  	
===  Properties ===

  	This component is not nillable.
---- 	
        
===  Model ===

	inclusive lower bound: -180inclusive upper bound: 180
